headline: Leidos (LDOS) Registers a Bigger Fall Than the Market: Important Facts to Note
summary: Leidos (LDOS) reached $162.09 at the closing of the latest trading day, reflecting a -1.44% change compared to its last close.

headline: Leidos Schedules Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call for August 5, 2025, at 8 a.m. (ET)
summary: Leidos (NYSE: LDOS) today announced it has scheduled a conference call for Tuesday, August 5, 2025, at 8 a.m. (ET) to announce its second quarter 2025 financial results for the period ending July 4, 2025, with the company planning to issue its quarterly earnings press release before the call.
